  [Text] Beijing, January 12 (XINHUA) -- Two Chinese leaders 
expressed condolences today on the death of Phoumi Vongvichit, 
member of the Advisory Committee of the Central Committee of the 
Lao People's Revolutionary Party and former acting president. 
  Ding Guangen, a member of the Political Bureau and 
