Phoumi Vongvichit, who was a member of the Advisory Committee of 
the Central Committee of the Lao People's Revolutionary Party, 
and a close friend of the CPC and the Chinese people." 
  Li wrote: "Heartfelt condolences on the passing of the 
Chinese people's close friend Comrade Phoumi Vongvichit." 

