Britain before negotiations on the Hong Kong airport can resume. 
The Foreign Ministry spokesman made the statement Thursday [20 
January] in Beijing during his weekly press conference. Our 
reporter Li Weiquan brings us up to date. 
  [Begin Li recording] [passage omitted] 
