Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, January 18 (XINHUA) -- Wan Li, former 
chairman of China's National People's Congress Standing 
Committee, is to be awarded an honorary doctorate by Johns 
Hopkins University of the U.S. this year. 
  This morning Wan met with Morris W. Offit, chairman of the 
board of trustees of the university, and his party at the Great 
Hall of the People. 
