  [Text] Munich, January 20 (XINHUA) -- Qiao Shi, chairman of 
China's National People's Congress (NPC) Standing Committee, 
arrived here this evening from Bonn via Stuttgart, capital of 
the Baden-Wuerttemberg State. 
  Upon their arrival here, Qiao and his wife Yu Wen and their 
