well-known 
German auto company -- Mercedes-Benz. 
  This morning, Qiao and his party attended a meeting in Bonn 
held by the German Federal Assembly. 
  Extending her warm welcome to Qiao Shi, Rita Suessmuth, 
president of the Federal Assembly, wished China peace, 
prosperity and greater successes in reform. 
  Qiao is paying an official goodwill visit to Germany at the 
invitation of Suessmuth. 

